---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Safety Assurance Global website visitors and customers.">
  <article>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Safety Assurance Global values your privacy and handles personal information in a responsible and transparent manner.</p>
    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect contact details and inquiry context that you voluntarily provide through direct communication channels.</p>
    <h2>How we use information</h2>
    <p>Information is used to respond to requests, provide services, and improve our website and client engagement experience.</p>
    <h2>Data handling</h2>
    <p>We maintain reasonable safeguards to protect data and limit access to authorized personnel only.</p>
    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <p>You may request updates or deletion of your personal information by contacting us at <a href="mailto:privacy@safetyassuranceglobal.com">privacy@safetyassuranceglobal.com</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
